## Installation

### Option 1: Standard Installation (Recommended)

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Zakir060/stochastic-transit-router.git
cd stochastic-transit-router
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel
pip install -e ".[dev,test,benchmarks,notebooks]"
pre-commit install
```

### Option 2: Minimal Installation (API only)

```bash
pip install stochastic-transit-router
```

### Option 3: Development Installation with All Extras

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev,test,benchmarks,notebooks,deployment]"
```

### Verification Checklist

```bash
# 1. Run tests
pytest tests/ -q

# 2. Check code quality
ruff check src/ tests/ scripts/
mypy src --strict

# 3. Verify API starts
uvicorn src.api.app:app --port 8000 &
curl http://localhost:8000/api/health
kill %1

# 4. Test CLI
python -m src.cli.main --help
```

### Troubleshooting Installation

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| **Python version error** | Ensure Python 3.12+: `python --version` |
| **pip not found** | Try `python -m pip` instead of `pip` |
| **Virtual environment issues** | Delete `.venv/` and recreate: `python -m venv .venv` |
| **Dependency conflicts** | Use `pip install --upgrade --force-reinstall -e .` |
| **Pre-commit hook errors** | Re-install: `pre-commit install --install-hooks` |

