## Advanced Features

### Reproducible Experiments

Every computation includes full provenance:

```json
{
  "run_id": "exp_2026-04-05_dijkstra_v1",
  "timestamp": "2026-04-05T14:32:00Z",
  "graph_version": "nyc_20260405.pkl",
  "algorithm": "dijkstra",
  "seed": 42,
  "python_version": "3.12.0",
  "platform": "Linux-x86_64",
  "results_hash": "a1b2c3d4e5f6...",
  "query_count": 1000,
  "mean_duration_ms": 48.3,
  "p95_duration_ms": 72.1
}
```

**Reproducibility guarantee:** Given same manifest, results are byte-for-byte identical

### Stochastic Routing (Future)

```python
# Planned API for uncertainty-aware routing
route = router.route(
    origin=123,
    destination=456,
    time=now(),
    confidence=0.95,  # 95% confidence interval
    risk_metric="CVaR"  # Conditional Value-at-Risk
)
# Returns: Route with 95% probability of on-time arrival
```

### Real-time Feed Integration (Scaffolded)

```python
# Monitor live delays
feeds = FeedManager()
status = feeds.check_status()
# {
#   "gtfs_realtime": {"healthy": true, "lag_seconds": 15},
#   "last_update": "2026-04-05T14:32:00Z"
# }

# Route with live data
route = router.route(origin=123, destination=456, include_realtime=True)
```

